Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.45,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\an9}迷い込んだ仮想世界は…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:34.41,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\an9}我 是光輝閃耀的黑白怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:37.43,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\an9}迷途走近假想的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫你那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說闇炎之主墜入了黑暗面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心又犯老毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者和邪王真眼是締結了戀人契約的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就當還給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點撒鹽 撒鹽 樟葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}註：撒鹽有淨化驅邪的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這種事情 哥哥你們不是不打算睡覺的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了 這也是魔王魔法少女的計謀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 說起來都是我們自己睡著了的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼現在開始銀杏學園高中極東魔術午睡結社之夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對紅葉岡高中午休同好會的練習比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(396,438)\fs21}Siesta
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有會贏的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就連是否醒著都無法辨別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無疑問是夢之世界的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和約好的一樣 輸了的話就請你們解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像玩笑似的自稱午睡社團的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能消失一個算一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼想也贏不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都睡得太多 皮膚都光滑光滑的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還剩下的最後手段是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在道歉的話還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不會輸的 這個社團不是那麼隨便的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初和六花相遇的時候就這麼想了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說我們真正的目的是探索不可視境界線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我們的活動將不會止步於此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我們的結社
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得能和六花她們一起做下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你說能一起這樣…對方可是中二病哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 總覺得雖然不怎麼能被大家理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是拚命努力 認真的地方和午睡部是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在極東魔術午睡結社之夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拚命努力地午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拚命努力地玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拚命努力地在Vanishment哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂吧 現實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綻開吧 神經突觸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vanishment this world！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個睡夢的世界是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿瓦隆粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Avalon Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷霆戰錘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mjolnir Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去資格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃闇炎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗的火焰當中…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去資格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳抽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去資格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟睡殺法 晝夜節律崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(457,438)\fs21}Circadian rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命運之輪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Destiny Ring
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 既然有如此巨大的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要認真起來以世界大賽為目標也不為過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 喜歡那個地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要保護那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三分醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Three Parts Wake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香學姐 茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 我們勝利了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 睡同學她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經回去了 她們說自己徹底輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 不用解散也行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:21:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 明天又能和冒牌森戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著的時候做了很有意思的夢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是夢嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個力量解放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃電衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Lighting Blast
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有這個 雷屬性的技能也完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要試 凸守也要試試
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年級的 你又在衣服上惡作劇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了呢 冒牌森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通用性好強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別做多餘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別東張西望的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.06,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是什麼都沒有改變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也根本不睡午覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是我覺得在這樣的環境中睡覺是最幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守 使用雷電攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好聽別人說話！
